article.description: — Tristan Enaruna totaled 24 points and 12 rebounds and Drew Lowder sank a jumper with one second left to rally Cleveland State to a 73-71 victory over Robert Morris on Sunday.
article.headline: Enaruna, Lowder rally Cleveland State past Robert Morris 73-71
article.linkText: Enaruna, Lowder rally Cleveland State past Robert Morris 73-71
article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- — Tristan Enaruna totaled 24 points and 12 rebounds and Drew Lowder sank a jumper with one second left to rally Cleveland State to a 73-71 victory over Robert Morris on Sunday. Tujautae Williams added 15 points and nine rebounds for the Vikings (17-12, 10-8 Horizon League). Lowder scored 10 on 5-for-15 shooting. Josh Corbin and Justice Williams scored 17 apiece to lead the Colonials (10-19, 6-12). Corbin added four assists. Markeese Hastings totaled 13 points, 10 rebounds and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
